{"tid":2261334,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★藍色招聘圈？勞工處灣仔辦大型招聘會　提供逾2500職位","createTime":"2020-10-28T08:28:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T13:53:28.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"790d04183110de7656b3965b1197a039fe6cb05d","tid":2261334,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T08:28:54.000Z","msg":"勞工處今明兩日在灣仔修頓室內場館舉行大型招聘會，46間機構提供超過2500個職位，涵蓋飲食、物業管理、零售等行業，八成三職位空缺為全職，大部分月薪介乎1.1萬至1.9萬元。 有市民提早來到等候入場，指菲律賓籍太太原本任職客戶服務員，但公司年初結業，疫情下即使將薪金目標下調三成，亦較難揾工，如在招聘會上有適合職位，希望即場面試。 有物業管理公司提供保安和大廈維修技工等12個類別職位，約40個空缺，負責人指有關職位對學歷要求不高，入行相對容易，預計可吸引想轉工的市民。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n招聘會及空缺詳情 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.jobs.gov.hk/1/0/jobfair/big5/2020-10-29-eippo.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.jobs.gov.hk%2F1%2F0%2Fjobfair%2Fbig5%2F2020-10-29-eippo.pdf&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7DMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=de6a8c7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.jobs.gov.hk/1/0/jobfair/big5/2020-10-29-eippo.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2363570\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2363570&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7DMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=d0deb5b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2363570</a>"},{"pid":"be5d18afe02e8bbc9111406680a98c8a2a2dfd7c","tid":2261334,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T08:29:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oHL8QSH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoHL8QSH.png&h=5555dc6a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZojNmZn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZojNmZn.png&h=b4c3e28a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fvBPAjo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfvBPAjo.png&h=5335faf8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"babc9678d64231c783f54780b01dbfd9c7a0